<h1>ASF Economic Impact Calculator</h1>
<p>This tool estimates direct economic losses caused by an African Swine Fever (ASF) outbreak.  
The model calculates costs from depopulation, compensation, laboratory testing, carcass disposal, official staff activity, and movement control.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Adjust Parameters</h2>

<div class="input-block">
    <label>Number of farms culled:</label><br>
    <input type="number" id="farmsCulled" value="10" min="0">
</div>

<div class="input-block">
    <label>Average pigs per farm:</label><br>
    <input type="number" id="pigsPerFarm" value="500" min="1">
</div>

<div class="input-block">
    <label>Compensation per pig (NTD):</label><br>
    <input type="number" id="compensation" value="8000" min="0">
</div>

